project_descr: Venezuelan CO has established a Development Advisory Services (DAS) Facility to provide direct support to upstream initiatives in UNDP’s Focus, mainly in the area of programmes/projects support.

outputs.output_descr: Venezuelan CO has established an Engagement Facility Project to provide direct support to upstream initiatives according to UNDP’s mandate and, mainly within the Country Program Document, CPD 2015-2019.

project_title: engagement facility project for venezuela co
